t; (107.29 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-6-10 11:08&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31952004&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=16955273136847a2f1f38cb2_64356869"/><published>2025-06-10T11:08:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3402d8830fdcecaae74d53d2211da268</id><title>深圳陶陶X</title><updated>2025-06-07T18:26:49+08:00</updated><author><name>sinchaubb</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-07T18:26:49+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572737724"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572737724"&gt;喺前海萬象城食嘅晚餐，上次經過已經想試，今晚就揀依間啦。&lt;br&gt;叫左好多野食，因為太好味，食到捧住個肚走&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;蒜蓉蒸乳山蠔、陳皮蒸鮑魚、大煲啫黃鱔、豬油渣炒菜心、梅菜乾炆豬手圈、蝦餃。全部都滿意，最好係唔會過咸，就算係炆豬手都係惹味、香，但係唔咸。&lt;br/&gt;蠔好肥美飽滿。鮑魚淋滑，無牙嗰位都咬到。黃鱔超級香。豬手軟滑充滿骨膠原，最重要唔會成塊皮都有毛。豬油渣炒菜心勁香。&lt;br/&gt;全部都好正，諗緊要唔要碗雙皮奶&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31949624&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=841&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-06-07T18:26:49+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>db522d81a2e095a17a347bf039ab42f0</id><title>會同古村</title><updated>2025-06-08T20:47:09+08:00</updated><author><name>timmywu</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-08T20:47:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572753625"&gt;&lt